\f0\b\fs26 \cf0 XBMC Media Center
\b0  is a free and open source cross-platform media-player and entertainment hub.\
\
XBMC supports a wide range of multimedia formats and includes features such as playlists, audio visualizations, slideshows, metadata retrieval, weather reporting, etc. In addition, it also supports an expanding array of third-party Python plugins.\
\
Please visit our official website located at {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://xbmc.org"}}{\fldrslt http://xbmc.org}} for more information. You will also find {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://wiki.xbmc.org/?title=XBMC_Online_Manual"}}{\fldrslt documentation}} and user support {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://forum.xbmc.org"}}{\fldrslt forums}} located there.}

